==History==
Accessories were intended to be released with the release of 2026.1.3, but during the open beta cycle, it was decided to delay its release until "it's ready for prime time". <ref>[https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/vrchat-202613 VRChat 2026.1.3] ([https://web.archive.org/web/20260325011753/https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/vrchat-202613 Archive.org]) on ''[https://docs.vrchat.com docs.vrchat.com]''. Dated March 24, 2026. Retrieved March 24, 2026.</ref> Accessories beta testing would continue alongside the regular Open Beta on a separate Steam beta branch.

